Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an3}Yeah 轻轻的告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:46.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an3}啊 已经迫不及待了
